Resource Profile: PT_Specimen

Official URL: http://hl7.pt/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/PTSpecimen Version: 0.0.1
Active as of 2024-09-23 Computable Name: PT_Specimen

A generic Specimen resource for Portugal

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: PT_DiagnosticReportLaboratory and PT_ServiceRequest
